# Private-only commits — never replayed to the public mirror.
#
# One commit SHA per line (short or full; matched against the source
# SHA of each format-patch). Inline `# …` comments and blank lines are
# ignored. Prefer adding `Private-Only: true` as a trailer on new
# commits — this file is the escape hatch for *already-merged* commits
# where amending the message is not an option without rewriting history.
#
# Format: <sha>[<whitespace># reason]

